{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":1531,"text":"I will always remember"},{"time":3776,"text":"the first time I met the girl\nin the blue uniform."},{"time":9577,"text":"I was eight at the time,"},{"time":12189,"text":"living in the village with my grandmother,"},{"time":15546,"text":"who was raising me and other children."},{"time":19538,"text":"Famine had hit my country of Zimbabwe,"},{"time":24236,"text":"and we just didn't have enough to eat."},{"time":28403,"text":"We were hungry."},{"time":31586,"text":"And that's when the girl\nin the blue uniform"},{"time":35101,"text":"came to my village with the United Nations"},{"time":38681,"text":"to feed the children."}]},{"cues":[{"time":41784,"text":"As she handed me my porridge,"},{"time":44387,"text":"I asked her why she was there,"},{"time":47672,"text":"and without hesitation, she said,"},{"time":51386,"text":"\"As Africans, we must uplift\nall the people of Africa.\""},{"time":59705,"text":"I had absolutely no idea what she meant."}]},{"cues":[{"time":62761,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":64856,"text":"But her words stuck with me."}]},{"cues":[{"time":68419,"text":"Two years later,"},{"time":69999,"text":"famine hit my country for the second time."},{"time":74514,"text":"My grandmother had no choice\nbut to send me to the city"},{"time":78999,"text":"to live with an aunt\nI had never met before."},{"time":83149,"text":"So at the age of 10,"},{"time":85031,"text":"I found myself in school\nfor the very first time."},{"time":90816,"text":"And there, at the city school,"},{"time":93483,"text":"I would experience\nwhat it was to be unequal."},{"time":98999,"text":"You see, in the village,"},{"time":100801,"text":"we were all equal."},{"time":103094,"text":"But in the eyes and the minds\nof the other kids,"},{"time":106285,"text":"I was not their equal."},{"time":109165,"text":"I couldn't speak English,"},{"time":111522,"text":"and I was way behind\nin terms of reading and writing."},{"time":117197,"text":"But this feeling of inequality\nwould get even more complex."},{"time":122999,"text":"Every school holiday"},{"time":124785,"text":"spent back in the village\nwith my grandmother"},{"time":127944,"text":"made me consciously aware"},{"time":130436,"text":"of the inequalities\nthis incredible opportunity"},{"time":133999,"text":"had created within my own family."},{"time":138086,"text":"Suddenly, I had much more\nthan the rest of my village."},{"time":143737,"text":"And in their eyes,\nI was no longer their equal."}]},{"cues":[{"time":149213,"text":"I felt guilty."},{"time":152530,"text":"But I thought about the girl\nin the blue uniform,"},{"time":156061,"text":"and I remember thinking,"},{"time":158348,"text":"\"That's who I want to be --"},{"time":161181,"text":"someone like her,"},{"time":163274,"text":"someone who uplifts other people.\""},{"time":167903,"text":"This childhood experience\nled me to the United Nations,"},{"time":172999,"text":"and to my current role with UN Women,"},{"time":175650,"text":"where we are addressing\none of the greatest inequalities"},{"time":179817,"text":"that affects more than half\nof the world's population --"},{"time":183786,"text":"women and girls."}]},{"cues":[{"time":186641,"text":"Today, I want to share with you"},{"time":188506,"text":"a simple idea that seeks to uplift\nall of us together."},{"time":197157,"text":"Eight months ago,"},{"time":198895,"text":"under the visionary leadership\nof Phumzile Mlambo-Ngcuka,"},{"time":203164,"text":"head of UN Women,"},{"time":205244,"text":"we launched a groundbreaking initiative"},{"time":208269,"text":"called HeForShe,"},{"time":210117,"text":"inviting men and boys\nfrom around the world"},{"time":213530,"text":"to stand in solidarity\nwith each other and with women,"},{"time":217872,"text":"to create a shared vision\nfor gender equality."},{"time":222054,"text":"This is an invitation\nfor those who believe in equality"},{"time":226999,"text":"for women and men,"},{"time":229284,"text":"and those who don't yet know\nthat they believe."}]},{"cues":[{"time":233935,"text":"The initiative is based on a simple idea:"},{"time":237999,"text":"that what we share is much more powerful"},{"time":242404,"text":"than what divides us."},{"time":244705,"text":"We all feel the same things."},{"time":247325,"text":"We all want the same things,"},{"time":250340,"text":"even when those things\nsometimes remain unspoken."},{"time":256356,"text":"HeForShe is about uplifting all of us,"},{"time":259102,"text":"women and men together."},{"time":261403,"text":"It's moving us towards\nan inflection point for gender equality."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266999,"text":"Imagine a blank page"},{"time":269174,"text":"with one horizontal line\nsplitting it in half."},{"time":273229,"text":"Now imagine that women\nare represented here,"},{"time":277427,"text":"and men are represented here."},{"time":281165,"text":"In our current population,"},{"time":283299,"text":"HeForShe is about moving\nthe 3.2 billion men,"},{"time":288711,"text":"one man at a time,"},{"time":290824,"text":"across that line,"},{"time":292649,"text":"so that ultimately,\nmen can stand alongside women"},{"time":297999,"text":"and be on the right side of history,"},{"time":300864,"text":"making gender equality a reality\nin the 21st century."}]},{"cues":[{"time":307348,"text":"However, engaging men in the movement\nwould prove quite controversial."},{"time":312999,"text":"Why invite men? They are the problem."}]},{"cues":[{"time":315872,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":317054,"text":"In fact, men don't care, we were told."}]},{"cues":[{"time":321387,"text":"But something incredible happened\nwhen we launched HeForShe."},{"time":326340,"text":"In just three days, more than 100,000 men"},{"time":331491,"text":"had signed up and committed\nto be agents of change for equality."},{"time":337999,"text":"Within that first week, at least one man\nin every single country in the world"},{"time":344451,"text":"stood up to be counted,"},{"time":347268,"text":"and within that same week,"},{"time":349641,"text":"HeForShe created more than\n1.2 billion conversations on social media."},{"time":357308,"text":"And that's when the emails\nstarted pouring in,"},{"time":361633,"text":"sometimes as many as a thousand a day."},{"time":367435,"text":"We heard from a man out of Zimbabwe,"},{"time":370514,"text":"who, after hearing about HeForShe,"},{"time":373205,"text":"created a \"husband school.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":375443,"text":"(Laughter)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":377760,"text":"He literally went around his village,"},{"time":380736,"text":"hand-picking all of the men\nthat were abusive to their partners,"},{"time":385022,"text":"and committed to turn them\ninto better husbands and fathers."},{"time":390625,"text":"In Pune, India, a youth advocate\norganized an innovative bicycle rally,"},{"time":396713,"text":"mobilizing 700 cyclists"},{"time":400372,"text":"to share the HeForShe messages\nwithin their own community."}]},{"cues":[{"time":405705,"text":"In another impact story,"},{"time":408514,"text":"a man sent a very personal note"},{"time":410943,"text":"of something that had happened\nin his own community."},{"time":414752,"text":"He wrote,"},{"time":417419,"text":"\"Dear Madam,"},{"time":419331,"text":"I have lived all of my life"},{"time":421991,"text":"next door to a man\nwho continuously beats up his wife."},{"time":427506,"text":"Two weeks ago,"},{"time":429069,"text":"I was listening to my radio,"},{"time":431800,"text":"and your voice came on,"},{"time":434236,"text":"and you spoke about something\ncalled the HeForShe,"},{"time":438780,"text":"and the need for men to play their role."},{"time":443023,"text":"Within a few hours, I heard\nthe woman cry again next door,"},{"time":448729,"text":"but for the first time,"},{"time":451173,"text":"I didn't just sit there."},{"time":453190,"text":"I felt compelled to do something,"},{"time":456999,"text":"so I went over\nand I confronted the husband."},{"time":461694,"text":"Madam, it has been two weeks,"},{"time":465084,"text":"and the woman has not cried since."},{"time":467909,"text":"Thank you for giving me a voice.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":470959,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":476166,"text":"Personal impact stories such as these"},{"time":479999,"text":"show that we are tapping\ninto something within men,"},{"time":484364,"text":"but getting to a world\nwhere women and men are equal"},{"time":487999,"text":"is not just a matter\nof bringing men to the cause."},{"time":492332,"text":"We want concrete, systematic,\nstructural change that can equalize"},{"time":499340,"text":"the political, economic\nand social realities for women and men."},{"time":505514,"text":"We are asking men\nto make concrete actions,"},{"time":508593,"text":"calling them to intervene\nat a personal level,"},{"time":511737,"text":"to change their behavior."},{"time":514165,"text":"We are calling upon governments,\nbusinesses, universities,"},{"time":519189,"text":"to change their policies."},{"time":522237,"text":"We want male leaders to become role models"},{"time":526443,"text":"and change agents\nwithin their own institutions."}]},{"cues":[{"time":531260,"text":"Already, a number of prominent men\nand leaders have stepped up"},{"time":535721,"text":"and made some concrete\nHeForShe commitments."},{"time":539292,"text":"In a few early success stories,"},{"time":542799,"text":"a leading French\nhospitality company, Accor,"},{"time":546363,"text":"has committed to eliminate the pay gap"},{"time":550063,"text":"for all of its 180,000 employees by 2020."}]},{"cues":[{"time":555459,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":559031,"text":"The government of Sweden,"},{"time":561491,"text":"under its current feminist government,"},{"time":564174,"text":"has committed to close\nboth the employment and the pay gap"},{"time":569357,"text":"for all of its citizens\nwithin the current electoral term."},{"time":574999,"text":"In Japan, the University of Nagoya"},{"time":578125,"text":"is building, as part of\ntheir HeForShe commitments,"},{"time":581404,"text":"what will become one of Japan's\nleading gender-research centers."}]},{"cues":[{"time":588665,"text":"Now, eight months later,"},{"time":591196,"text":"a movement is building."},{"time":594030,"text":"We are seeing men sign up\nfrom every single walk of life,"},{"time":598999,"text":"and from every single corner in the world,"},{"time":602373,"text":"from the United Nations' own\nSecretary-General Ban Ki-moon"},{"time":606579,"text":"to the Secretary-Generals of NATO\nand the EU Council,"},{"time":612221,"text":"from the prime minister of Bhutan"},{"time":614822,"text":"to the president of Sierra Leone."}]},{"cues":[{"time":618068,"text":"In Europe alone,\nall the male EU Commissioners"},{"time":622210,"text":"and the members of Parliament\nof the Swedish and Iceland governments"},{"time":626330,"text":"have signed up to be HeForShe."},{"time":629464,"text":"In fact, one in 20 men in Iceland\nhas joined the movement."},{"time":636681,"text":"The rallying call of our passionate\ngoodwill ambassador, Emma Watson,"},{"time":641237,"text":"has garnered more than\nfive billion media impressions,"},{"time":645190,"text":"mobilizing hundreds and thousands\nof students around the world"},{"time":650215,"text":"to create more than a hundred\nHeForShe student associations."}]},{"cues":[{"time":656118,"text":"Now this is the beginning\nof the vision that HeForShe has"},{"time":661341,"text":"for the world that we want to see."},{"time":665079,"text":"Einstein once said,"},{"time":667865,"text":"\"A human being is part of the whole ..."},{"time":672523,"text":"but he experiences himself,"},{"time":675262,"text":"his thoughts and feelings,"},{"time":677357,"text":"as something separate from the rest ..."},{"time":680725,"text":"This delusion\nis a kind of prison for us ..."},{"time":684856,"text":"Our task must be\nto free ourselves from this prison"},{"time":689840,"text":"by widening our circle of compassion.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":694982,"text":"If women and men\nare part of a greater whole,"},{"time":698475,"text":"as Einstein suggests,"},{"time":700999,"text":"it is my hope that HeForShe\ncan help free us to realize"},{"time":706276,"text":"that it is not our gender that defines us,"},{"time":710951,"text":"but ultimately, our shared humanity."},{"time":715015,"text":"HeForShe is tapping\ninto women's and men's dreams,"},{"time":719532,"text":"the dreams that we have for ourselves,"},{"time":722570,"text":"and the dreams that we have\nfor our families, our children,"},{"time":727499,"text":"friends, communities."}]},{"cues":[{"time":731078,"text":"So that's what it is about."},{"time":734776,"text":"HeForShe is about uplifting\nall of us together."}]},{"cues":[{"time":742086,"text":"Thank you."}]},{"cues":[{"time":743269,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}